{"id":128055,"type":6,"name":"亲亲我，老师","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/8f/c6/128055_EwB85.jpg","summary":"　　夏天到了，幼儿园准备放暑假，小朋友们要被各自的家长接回家去，老师们也准备集体到海滨度假。假日第二天，大部分老师愉快踏上了休假旅程，只有苗苗（黄禾 饰）老师自愿留下来等待部分迟来的家长，然后再去度假。结果传来消息，有三个小朋友的家长因各种原因不能来接孩子了，苗苗也错过了出行的列车。当时幼儿园只剩下厨师达达（宁文彤 饰）和收发室的杨爷爷（杨子纯 饰），他们三人只好陪着三个孩子待在园里过这个暑假。三个孩子都是四岁，他们是贪吃的陈晨，多动的罗犀子，还有小女孩春雪，在这三大三小的六个人身上，会发生怎样的故事呢......","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>亲亲我，老师</li><li><span>别名: </span>親親我老師</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>亲亲我老师</li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>1990</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 儿童</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>每集长: </span>28min</li><li><span>导演: </span>杨韬</li><li><span>编剧: </span>诸葛怡</li><li><span>主演: </span>苗苗 / 陈晨 / 罗犀子 / 郝春雪 / 达达</li>","eps":[{"id":500430,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500430","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500431,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500431","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500432,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500432","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500433,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500433","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500434,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500434","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500435,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500435","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500436,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500436","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500437,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500437","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}]}